266
00:17:55,360 --> 00:17:57,400
Bukankah kau paling suka mendengar cerita?

267
00:17:59,040 --> 00:18:00,280
Jangan tidur lagi.

268
00:18:01,320 --> 00:18:02,600
Aku akan menceritakan kisah untukmu.

269
00:18:04,360 --> 00:18:05,560
Bangunlah,

270
00:18:07,320 --> 00:18:08,320
oke?

271
00:18:23,640 --> 00:18:24,800
Berhasil.

272
00:18:29,320 --> 00:18:30,560
Adik.

273
00:18:30,640 --> 00:18:32,720
Apakah kau mendengar
perkataan pujaan hatimu?

274
00:18:34,760 --> 00:18:36,240
Mimpinya sudah berakhir.

275
00:18:37,280 --> 00:18:38,760
Cepatlah bangun.

276
00:18:48,560 --> 00:18:49,800
Ternyata benar.

277
00:18:49,880 --> 00:18:52,920
Tetap harus pujaan hati
yang bisa membangunkannya.

278
00:18:56,760 --> 00:18:57,720
Gawat!

279
00:18:57,800 --> 00:18:59,120
- Gawat!
- Tenang!

280
00:18:59,200 --> 00:19:00,160
Gawat!

281
00:19:00,240 --> 00:19:02,160
Su Jian, mengapa kau masih di sini?

282
00:19:02,240 --> 00:19:03,200
Cepat lihat!

283
00:19:03,280 --> 00:19:04,760
Ibumu berebut air dengan orang-orang

284
00:19:04,840 --> 00:19:06,320
